The paper deals with recommending appropriate conferences to authors based on the content of their paper and the social network of the authors. This involves techniques such as dimensionality reduction and topic modeling. The paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category as it deals with recommending appropriate conferences based on the content of the paper. It could also belong to the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category as it involves the use of social networks of authors. Additionally, the paper involves techniques such as dimensionality reduction and topic modeling, which are commonly used in sub-categories such as Deep Learning (cs.DL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL).
